TIL I learned Walgreens purposely hires people with disabilities to work in their warehouses. The warehouses are designed to enable people with disabilities to be a valuable team member..
My uncle works for the service who apparently must line these disabled people up with walgreens, he's always saying how amazing it is to watch them feel useful and fulfilled.
